547
00:32:34.770 --> 00:32:37.917
Oh. I read
your book.

548
00:32:38.670 --> 00:32:40.545
I know how bad off
your heart is.

549
00:32:40.658 --> 00:32:42.427
You really need it.

550
00:32:44.165 --> 00:32:48.379
Did you know
electromagnetic fields

551
00:32:48.488 --> 00:32:51.239
