function of a pacemaker?

552
00:32:51.360 --> 00:32:53.364
No! No! No!

553
00:32:53.481 --> 00:32:55.156
Shh!

554
00:32:55.551 --> 00:32:58.171
All you have to do is watch.
You have the easy part. Jenny.

555
00:32:58.690 --> 00:33:04.413
but your brother.
he is probably

556
