580
00:34:14.190 --> 00:34:20.707
Do you even understand love.
Ryan. real love?

581
00:34:31.924 --> 00:34:35.035
Oh. Your fingers are blue.

582
00:34:35.143 --> 00:34:37.525
Your blood's not circulating.

583
00:34:46.626 --> 00:34:48.662
