I got calls. e-mails.

623
00:37:50.601 --> 00:37:52.330
I thought it was
on a secure server.

624
00:37:52.425 --> 00:37:53.571
Yeah. but if there's
a bump or delay

625
00:37:53.677 --> 00:37:56.348
